    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    Found these on the Bandits that spawn by Warslicks Woods zone from Feild of Bone...no idea what they are for....got about 10 of them :).They con blue to my lvl 15<br><br>

Oggie....and cast buffs like mad, Root, wind gust, they heal...these arev bad asses....any ideas on what these things are for?<br><br>

These things look like a red sash, belt slot and drop off of them allmost all of the time. they also drop brozne weapons, ushually spears....i have been hunting these guys for about a week now.....just started to drop the sash 2 days ago..Oct 26, anyways thats the skinny :)<br><br>

Raraka lvl 7 SHM (Imortalis)_</font>
